{
  "text": "OK. I'm sort of hunting around here for an entry into some information. I may not be looking in a productive area. But you had stated that \"we (that is Ra) had been aided by shapes such as the pyramid, so that we could aid your people with a shape such as the pyramid. \" These shapes have been mentioned many, many times and you have also stated that the shapes themselves aren't of too much consequence. I see a relation between these shapes and the energies that we have been studying with respect to the body, and I would like to ask a few questions on the pyramid to see if I might get an entry into some of this understanding. You stated, \"You will find the intersection of the triangle which is at the first level on each of the four sides forms a diamond in a plane which is horizontal. \" Can you tell me what you meant by the word, intersection? I am Ra. Your mathematics and arithmetic have a paucity of configurative descriptions which we might use. Without intending to be obscure, we may note that the purpose of the shapes is to work with time/space portions of the mind/body/spirit complex. Therefore, the intersection is both space/time and time/space oriented and thus is expressed in three dimensional geometry by two intersections which, when projected in both time/space and space/time, form one point.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "OK.",
        "start_offset": 0,
        "end_offset": 3,
        "start": 12.921,
        "end": 12.981
      },
      {
        "segment": "I'm sort of hunting around here for an entry into some information.",
        "start_offset": 4,
        "end_offset": 71,
        "start": 13.121,
        "end": 20.422
      },
      {
        "segment": "I may not be looking in a productive area.",
        "start_offset": 72,
        "end_offset": 114,
        "start": 20.542,
        "end": 23.962
      },
      {
        "segment": "But you had stated that \"we (that is Ra) had been aided by shapes such as the pyramid, so that we could aid your people with a shape such as the pyramid.",
        "start_offset": 115,
        "end_offset": 268,
        "start": 25.542,
        "end": 41.564
      },
      {
        "segment": "These shapes have been mentioned many, many times and you have also stated that the shapes themselves aren't of too much consequence.",
        "start_offset": 271,
        "end_offset": 404,
        "start": 41.844,
        "end": 52.685
      },
      {
        "segment": "I see a relation between these shapes and the energies that we have been studying with respect to the body, and I would like to ask a few questions on the pyramid to see if I might get an entry into some of this understanding.",
        "start_offset": 405,
        "end_offset": 631,
        "start": 54.705,
        "end": 70.727
      },
      {
        "segment": "You stated, \"You will find the intersection of the triangle which is at the first level on each of the four sides forms a diamond in a plane which is horizontal.",
        "start_offset": 632,
        "end_offset": 793,
        "start": 75.127,
        "end": 89.429
      },
      {
        "segment": "Can you tell me what you meant by the word, intersection?",
        "start_offset": 796,
        "end_offset": 853,
        "start": 90.109,
        "end": 93.009
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 854,
        "end_offset": 862,
        "start": 100.73,
        "end": 102.67
      },
      {
        "segment": "Your mathematics and arithmetic have a paucity of configurative descriptions which we might use.",
        "start_offset": 863,
        "end_offset": 959,
        "start": 106.09,
        "end": 134.693
      },
      {
        "segment": "Without intending to be obscure, we may note that the purpose of the shapes is to work with time/space portions of the mind/body/spirit complex.",
        "start_offset": 960,
        "end_offset": 1104,
        "start": 137.353,
        "end": 181.237
      },
      {
        "segment": "Therefore, the intersection is both space/time and time/space oriented and thus is expressed in three dimensional geometry by two intersections which, when projected in both time/space and space/time, form one point.",
        "start_offset": 1105,
        "end_offset": 1321,
        "start": 183.138,
        "end": 246.984
      }
    ],
